Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}流动的水没有形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}漂流的风找不到踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}任何案件的推理都取决于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.59,0:00:09.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}一堆令人向往的超级车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}天价的名车却隐藏复杂的心思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}唯一揭开事情的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.63,0:00:14.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}外表看似小孩，头脑却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他的名字就叫...名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}正因为你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:30.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喜好不同 脚程与表达的方式也大异其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.46,0:00:37.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如今我们在两人的记忆中正在渐渐褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我摸索过 却开始探寻其他人与未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.27,0:00:52.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我比自己想象的活的更坚强 追寻一种特别的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.41,0:00:56.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为难以应付的每一天所苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}true heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.69,0:01:07.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为了不再迷惑 请别松开你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使是互相伤害的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.07,0:01:21.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是一直在迷惘的时空中找寻答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.68,0:01:27.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝着下一个舞台 you take you way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请抱紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:38.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.67,0:01:46.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}197 超级汽车陷井(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.37,0:01:52.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}还可以看到海呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，叔叔呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.41,0:02:00.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}奇怪了，刚才还一起走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.54,0:02:05.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂~你们别顾着自已休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.37,0:02:09.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的，虽然是一等奨的奨品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是这种没有交通工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.45,0:02:14.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}又是深山里的旅馆，真的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}爸爸，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.50,0:02:22.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}旅馆怎么这么远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.54,0:02:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}根本完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.54,0:02:29.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要是二等奖的刷刷锅就好了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.37,0:02:34.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k75}讨厌，不要说这种煞风景的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是你告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.45,0:02:38.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}什么时候才能到那间旅馆呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}就快到了，加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.58,0:02:46.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看那间旅馆应该就是了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请在住宿卡上做登记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，毛利...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.58,0:03:00.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生，房间是201号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，这间旅馆是很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}不过没考虑过做接送巴士吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要这样，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}真是很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}现在让我带你们到房间去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.50,0:03:19.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}麻烦你了，走吧柯南...咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.41,0:03:22.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南 你在那里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.58,0:03:27.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊~好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好酷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}柯南 你在这里做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的，到处乱跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}你们看，好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这里有很多老式跑车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}这是捷克XK120
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这加长的车头还有它的线条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}是它的特征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}看起来就像豹的身现一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.66,0:03:59.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在还是很多捷克迷的梦想车呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是宾士300SL 卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}卡恩就像海鸥的翅膀一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}打开车门的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.54,0:04:17.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}就像海鸥展翅一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.41,0:04:22.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}咦，那是凯迪拉克吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对 凯迪拉克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}是53年的CB
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.54,0:04:28.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}它拥有最棒的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}也被称为美国究极的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为只生产500辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以很快就被买光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.66,0:04:40.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在在同好之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这已经变成了传说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小男孩，你知道的还真详细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.79,0:04:51.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这里是新成立的跑车展示窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}本旅管的老板是个超级跑车迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为了这个展示厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.62,0:05:01.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}还特地将旅馆做了改造呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.70,0:05:05.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，最里面是空的耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}恩，那个空间是用来放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}社长的爱车法拉利迪诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦，法拉利迪诺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.62,0:05:16.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}不会是206GD吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是....那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k84}柯南，那是怎样的车呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}全世界只有生产152辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}就算现在想买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}差不多已经是不可能的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}迪诺就是法拉利的创始者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}安泽法拉利的独子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}亚伦迪诺的简称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他在24岁就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}不过生前参与开发的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就装置在这辆车子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.75,0:05:49.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以安泽就将自己的爱子之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用在车子上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}原来还有这个典故啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}胜昌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}接待人员离开接待处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}还有，客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}这个展示埸在明天开幕之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.62,0:06:09.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}是禁止进入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.83,0:06:14.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.62,0:06:26.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个客人，难道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社长，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然这辆车比生命还要宝贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过从东京开到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}还是会累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社氞，其也的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}已经放在展示埸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}社长的车子也可以马上开过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}等等，不用那么急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}今晚我想和它共度一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为开始展示之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:04.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}就不能像这样自由自在的驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社长，其实请看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}嗯?侦探...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:14.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么回事?只有一张床啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}别那么奢求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:19.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}免费住已经要谢天谢地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这种床怎么能睡的下三个人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我要他们帮我们换房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}有什么关系，睡沙发就行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:30.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}大叔还是那么天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}放心，包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}明天下午三点就会开幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以今晚是最后的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}对，你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}按照计划去做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.75,0:07:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南，你过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}放开我，小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}不要闹了，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.75,0:07:57.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}反正这旅馆又没人住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我一定要他们换房间给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}但是如果这样做的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}可能会被收追加费用吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}而且如果再那么吵的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}可能会被赶出这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}恐吓信?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.87,0:08:18.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.66,0:08:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k79}别开展示埸，不然要你后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那封恐吓言是几天前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.83,0:08:31.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家正在商量要怎么处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这封恐吓信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}的确有点魄力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}这会不会是单纯的恶作剧呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果是这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}我希望你能在明天开幕之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}替我做护卫，可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们想藉助名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}毛利先生的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有没有报警?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果您愿意答应的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我愿意提供本旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}最豪华的这个房间给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这贵宾房吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}知道了，我接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}这样我也可以安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:16.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}请大家就像坐在大船里，放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了，兰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}等用完晚餐之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.87,0:09:38.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}要不要坐我的车去游车河?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃，可以坐迪诺吗?太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔，我也可以去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:51.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}爸爸，我也可以去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.08,0:09:55.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真美味，这牛排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}实在太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.87,0:09:58.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我还要再来一盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好，撒到你了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}没关系，我是服务人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸，你喝太多了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社长，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.87,0:10:16.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}在展示埸的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}什...什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}别阻止  别阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}冷静点，大竹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.91,0:10:24.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}别妨碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.04,0:10:32.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}放开我，随我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.12,0:10:33.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你不要乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.95,0:10:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}啰唆!我要毁掉这辆车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大竹先生，为什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.95,0:10:43.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}这不是你最宝贵的车子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.16,0:10:43.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k71}呃，要伤害自己的车子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大竹先生，你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.20,0:10:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你怎么可能会了解我的心情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}举办这种...这种展示埸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.91,0:11:03.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}我要毁掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.91,0:11:14.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这辆车子，53年的CB
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.95,0:11:18.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}是我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为了朝着这个梦想前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}我从早做到晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.00,0:11:25.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}终于可以得到这辆车子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然这么重要的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}为什么还要毁掉它呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}既然要我放弃这辆车的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我情愿亲手将它给毁掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.08,0:11:35.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}...我是这样想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.87,0:11:39.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k79}放弃?怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.08,0:11:42.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么回事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.12,0:11:45.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}问在那里的寺泉就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}寺泉先生，到底是怎么回事 ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.12,0:11:51.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这实在是天大的误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大竹先生，你应该感谢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}不应该恨我才对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你要我感谢你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}要开这展示会的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}根本没人会高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}除了你以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.04,0:12:09.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}大竹先生怎么会明白失去爱车的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我十分了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.04,0:12:15.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}没有人会高兴开这展示会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.95,0:12:20.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k104}对不起，请问你们是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我和大竹先生一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.04,0:12:26.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}必须放弃这宾士的相良新介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.25,0:12:29.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是龟冈丈二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}那车捷克的前一住主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}我们三人都是被那里的寺泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.16,0:12:37.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把车子给骗走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.16,0:12:39.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你怎么可以这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}这是你们自食恶果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.16,0:12:45.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们说被骗...这到底是怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们3人虽然是小公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}但是 都是个经营者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是旅行代理店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}我是不动产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我是汽车修理厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.08,0:12:58.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}但是在这种不景气的情况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}大家都出现经营上的困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}结果在那里的寺泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}就说以这些车子做抵押
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}愿意借钱给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.20,0:13:11.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当然我们接受了他的提议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但这是个陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.20,0:13:17.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}我们是后来才知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}都是那个男人从中作梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}抢走了我们的生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.12,0:13:24.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}结果最后日期到了还是无法还钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}车子就这样被抢走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.12,0:13:29.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}寺泉一开始就想抢走我们的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.20,0:13:33.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以才用金钱让我们中计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说得还真像是真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.25,0:13:41.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你有证据证明我陷害你们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果你们有时间去胡思乱想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}不如想怎么还钱更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要你们还钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}车子随时都可以还给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你说什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}啍，想吓唬我也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.12,0:13:57.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}原来如此，那封恐吓信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来是你们写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}恐吓信?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}别装蒜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}不管你们怎么阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.04,0:14:09.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}我都会如期开幕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}相良先生的鞋子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}放心，包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.25,0:14:22.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}明天下午三点就会举行开幕典礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以今晚是最后的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.29,0:14:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}对，不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.29,0:14:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}照计划去做就对了，知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请问相良先生住几号房呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}202号房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}怎么，我的房间有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}不，是因为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}300SL实在太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.29,0:14:56.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}想今晚跑去找你聊一聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，今晚不行 我有事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}跟你没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.29,0:15:09.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说...说得也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}酒店服务?我们没叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}会不会是搞错了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}不，因为你们是社长的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以这是本旅馆送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果还有什么需要的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}请不用客气的说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.12,0:15:28.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}是吗，那么给我一瓶红酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}最好是波尔多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.20,0:15:34.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}爸爸，不要这样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.45,0:15:40.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了，刚才很抱歉弄脏你的裤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:44.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我己经换过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.45,0:15:47.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}迪诺的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.37,0:15:51.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}的确听到一些引擎的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不会错，是迪诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.33,0:15:59.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社长，这么晚你要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为那些家伙毁了我今天的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}我要出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}寺泉先生，今晚的雾很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}还是不要出去比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}在这车子里面总比和那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:19.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}住在同一个旅馆里面更加安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请小心驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.37,0:16:31.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}经理，社长还没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的，已经九点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.41,0:16:59.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}社长到底跑到哪里去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还没有回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.41,0:17:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过下午三点才开幕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}应该还来得及吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}迪诺还要摆到展示埸去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.33,0:17:19.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}下午我们也要开始接待客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.45,0:17:22.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过完全没有连络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}这实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}寺泉还没有回来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}龟冈先生 大竹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.45,0:17:33.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}万一遇到突发事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天大概无法进行开幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}这是天谴  天谴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.37,0:17:41.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}社长先生有没有带手机?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，对了，我完全忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.45,0:17:48.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}让我来告诉他别让别人担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.58,0:17:52.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好好的跟他说教一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，是社长吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}是我，毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你现在在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.37,0:18:02.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}啊...这里是什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么一片漆黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.37,0:18:07.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}一片漆黑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，社长? 社长?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}他用很痛苦的声音说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}这里是哪里，怎么一片漆黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接者就断线了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.41,0:18:23.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}漆黑...外面大雾应该是白色的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.62,0:18:28.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生，漆黑是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}经理，已经十点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}今天的准备工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}再不开始就来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也对，那就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:47.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看来 今天的开幕典礼是开不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.41,0:18:54.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}中止，一定是遭天谴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.41,0:18:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}变成和恐吓信一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:02.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.50,0:19:07.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小兰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.37,0:19:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小兰姊姊，小兰姊姊在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.54,0:19:14.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南，我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.66,0:19:19.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小兰姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:25.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小兰姊姊，怎么了?没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯，我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}小兰，怎么了，小兰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起，我出来散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}结果在雾中突然有人叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}害我吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你不是野田警卫吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你在这里做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}其实是这位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}在雾中正往悬崖方向走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我觉得很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}才会叫住她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}然后她突然大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.45,0:19:58.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}真是令人担心的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，有车子的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}社长终于回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}不，那声音不是社长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.50,0:20:07.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}是相良先生的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.58,0:20:12.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么了，大家都在一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的耶，听声音就知道是哪辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.58,0:20:24.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}实在太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.62,0:20:27.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这里的常客大部分都能认出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.62,0:20:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么我继续去巡逻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}相良先生，你昨晚去哪里了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.66,0:20:39.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}啊，到附近逛了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}途中有没有看到社长的车子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k95}你退后一点，我要把车子开到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.54,0:20:49.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}停车埸去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊，经理，现在要展示迪诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.54,0:20:55.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}可能已经来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}不管怎么，现在最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}就是社长现在身在何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}找不到他的话根本什么也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.54,0:21:06.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}喂，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}寺泉他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}在车里的寺泉样子有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.66,0:21:16.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃! 什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.58,0:21:29.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}寺泉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.75,0:21:30.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}快找医生 快叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.58,0:21:37.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}没用的  他已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.66,0:21:46.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死因是二氧化碳中毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.83,0:21:48.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为引擎一直启动者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}使的车内充满废气瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想大概是废气瓦斯逆流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.58,0:21:56.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}跑进车子里面了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这应该是意外死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:02.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}窗户有点微开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.58,0:22:06.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}这到底是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.87,0:22:09.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么，为何窗户会微开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.70,0:22:12.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}这真的是....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.70,0:22:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}意外死亡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.79,0:22:37.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不知道　该用什么话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才能告诉你我真正的感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.24,0:22:53.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}从那时起　不知过了多少季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.19,0:22:59.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然时间无情地流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.16,0:23:06.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你却总是　微笑地陪着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.84,0:23:17.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我没对你说出口的  至今还有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Secret of my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}请你不要怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.29,0:23:28.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}无论何时　只要还有少许未来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.46,0:23:33.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真相　是紧握在手中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.49,0:23:39.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I can't say
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.49,0:23:39.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}I'm waiting for a chance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.49,0:23:39.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}请给我点时间
